{
  "texts": [
    "In contrast, our encodings are trained with metric learning and learn to suppress visual artifacts without any supervision.",
    "In the preceding, we have emphasized the replacement of traditional computer vision by our approach.",
    "In reality, the approaches are complementary and can be combined.",
    "This is already assumed by the present paper, as our pipeline is applied only after the images have been coarsely aligned using traditional computer vision approaches (Methods).",
    "Although our approach does not require a global spring mesh extending over all sections, an elastic regularizer is used for 2D patches during SEAMLeSS training and by the Online Field Finetuner at runtime."
  ]
}